{"word":"δανείζω","slug":"δανείζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δανείζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>δάνος</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to put out money at usury, to lend</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to have lent to one, to borrow</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>ἐπὶ μεγάλοις τόκοις</el> at high interest, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, of the money, <i>to be lent out</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}